cockpit-upside (1.0.0) noble; urgency=medium

  * Control: instant commands (upscmd, risk-tiered with a danger zone),
    writable variables (upsrw Configuration view), and clean shutdown on low
    battery (upsmon Shutdown step + per-UPS settings, opt-in killpower).
  * Event notifications (upsmon NOTIFY) via a pluggable adapter that defaults
    to the system mailer.
  * Guided setup wizard (NUT modes) covering USB / SNMP / serial devices, and
    one-click "enable history" (PCP).
  * Per-UPS Manage menu, remote-upsd (name@host) support, and a version
    indicator.

 -- Robert Sæther <robert4832@pm.me>  Mon, 01 Jun 2026 20:37:58 +0000

cockpit-upside (0.1.0) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial release: UPS monitoring for Cockpit, powered by NUT.
    Overview + per-device detail, friendly names, optional PCP trends,
    and a navigation status indicator.

